  <scopecontent id="aspace_a69ee49d2e8bd256ba25f011695ea2bf">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>The collection consists of material of a homoerotic nature assembled by Gordon Martin, and includes typescripts and photocopies of erotic/pornographic short prose fictions, a few of which are illustrated with drawings or photographs; catalogs and brochures of mail order enterprises dealing in erotica and pornography; and erotic and pornographic films.</p>  </scopecontent>
